of the use of or inability to use this software.

INDEMNIFICATION:
Users agree to indemnify and hold harmless the Royal Papua New Guinea Police Force
from and against any claims, damages, losses, and expenses arising out of the use
of this software.

TERMINATION:
This license may be terminated immediately upon violation of any terms or upon
